message.entry: Setting properties on object-arrays is not supported during codegen.\nUse a for-loop instead.
Accessing properties on object-arrays is not supported during codegen.\nUse cellfun(@(i)objArr(i).{0},num2cell(1:numel(objArr)),UniformOutput=false)
Calling methods on object-arrays is not supported.\nUse cellfun(@(i)objArr(i).{0}(arg1,...,argn),num2cell(1:numel(objArr)),UniformOutput=false)
